      "cue_start_seconds": 18.778,
      "id": "beat_03",
      "narration_text": "On January 27, NASA did not ask Thiokol to prove launch was safe. It asked them to prove it was unsafe.",
      "render_as": "motion",
      "scene_id": "scene_challenger_beat_03_burden_shift"
    },
    {
